data.description: Huge opportunity to become the owner of this beautiful property. House is owner occupied. Amazing opportunity at an exceptional price! Features a gas log fireplace in the main living area, a beautiful skylight in the kitchen directly above the island with granite countertop on all surfaces, a large den at the immediate entrance, and a home office to the right of the entrance with potential to be a fourth room!  This 2,449 sq ft home, sitting on .29 acres in the sought-after Lakewood Forest subdivision truly has a beautiful layout with a lot of potential to be your forever home. Claim it before it’s gone!
